<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Business Rejection Notification</title>
        <style type="text/css">
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                min-width: 100%;
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 1.5;
                background-color: #fafafa;
                color: #222;
            }
            a {
                color: #000;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
                font-weight: 700;
                line-height: 1.25;
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            p {
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 24px;
            }
            .email-wrapper {
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }
            .email-header {
                background-color: #f44336;
                padding: 24px;
                color: #fff;
                text-align: center;
            }
            .email-body {
                padding: 24px;
                background-color: #fff;
            }
            .email-footer {
                background-color: #f6f6f6;
                padding: 24px;
                text-align: center;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="email-wrapper">
            <div class="email-header">
                <h1>Academix Business Rejected</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="email-body">
                <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
                <p>We regret to inform you that your business application for "<strong><%= businessName %></strong>" has been <strong>rejected</strong> after a careful review.</p>
                <p>The reason for rejection may include missing or invalid information, or not meeting our platform criteria.</p>
                <% if (reason) { %>
                    <p><strong>Reason provided:</strong> <%= reason %></p>
                <% } %>
                <p>If you believe this decision was made in error, or if you would like to reapply, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
                <p>Thank you for your interest in Academix.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="email-footer">
                <p>Need help? Reach us at <a href="mailto:support@academix.com">support@academix.com</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
